Have you played Baba is You?

The general idea is that there's a set number of key words, usually conjunctions- Is, Not, And being the primary ones. By using those conjunctions to string together logical arguments- Baba is You, for example- you change certain elements of the level. The phrase I gave as an example is what gives you, the player, control over Baba.

And it just gets more complicated from there.
